headline: GQR Partners with Turbin.ai to Launch Workday Talent Marketplace
summary: GQR, a global leader in specialized talent acquisition and a trusted Workday® Staffing, AMS, Advisory, and Innovation partner, today announced a strategic partnership with Turbin.ai to launch the GQR x Turbin Workday Talent Marketplace, a platform designed to give Workday customers and partners direct access to elite, pre-vetted consultants.
